import { Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import { Layout } from "antd";
import { FormProvider, FormStatusProvider } from "./utils/FormState";
import { BookingStatusProvider } from "./utils/BookingState";
import {
  Navbar,
  Home,
  Login,
  SignUp,
  Screening,
  Results,
  Booking,
  Footerbar,
  Result,
} from "./components";
import Amplify from "aws-amplify";
import config from "./aws-exports";
import { StyledFooter } from "./components/Styles/Footer.style";
import { AuthStatusProvider } from "./utils/AuthState";
import Verification from "./components/Authentication/Verification/Verification";

Amplify.configure(config);

const { Header, Content } = Layout;

const App = () => {
  return (
    <AuthStatusProvider>
      <FormProvider>
        <FormStatusProvider>
          <BookingStatusProvider>
            <Layout>
              <Header>
                <Navbar />
              </Header>
              <Content>
                <Switch>
                  <Route exact path="/">
                    <Home />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/login">
                    <Login />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/signup">
                    <SignUp />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/verification">
                    <Verification />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/screening">
                    <Screening />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/results">
                    <Results />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/result">
                    <Result />
                  </Route>
                  <Route exact path="/booking">
                    <Booking />
                  </Route>
                </Switch>
              </Content>
              <StyledFooter>
                <Footerbar />
              </StyledFooter>
            </Layout>
          </BookingStatusProvider>
        </FormStatusProvider>
      </FormProvider>
    </AuthStatusProvider>
  );
};

export default App;
